{"lastModified":1772813157925,"uri":"c::9333113412::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Papua New Guinea, Maluku, Lesser Sunda Islands\n\nTimeless Craftmanship & Luxury Meets Adventure\n\nSequoia is an intimate, cosy, safe, and state-of-the-art vessel sailing through the stunning waters of Indonesia. Her Owner dedicated four years to overseeing her bespoke build, resulting in a 30-metre, hand-crafted wooden schooner designed to explore the 18,000-island archipelago. \n\nBlending timeless craftsmanship with modern marine technology, Sequoia has safety and ecological consciousness at the core of her design. Sequoia is equipped with low consumption systems and advanced sanitation to minimise her carbon footprint, and silent running under sail is enabled by cutting-edge materials. Single-use plastics are no longer used onboard for an eco-friendly cruising experience. \n\nSequoia guides guests through Indonesia’s Coral Triangle, a region brimming with life, beauty, and wonder. Each Sequoia Safari embodies the art of living, offering warmth, intimacy, and a spirit of connection.","blueprint":{"name":"SEQUOIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bb5795d0-e4ce-11ef-b336-a13e87fc9e92/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bb57bce0-e4ce-11ef-9e28-c76e48bc3499/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf089a70-e4cf-11ef-a365-a5422444b858/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bb340840-e4ce-11ef-a365-a5422444b858/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bb58ce50-e4ce-11ef-8e28-3b5186bcca16/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23fe-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bb4657c0-e4ce-11ef-a365-a5422444b858/{imageVariant}","/me